data.description:
This gorgeous modern farmhouse features all the upgrades that you deserve!!  Gorgeous luxury wood laminate throughout main living areas. Sleek and stylish gourmet kitchen with island and custom soft close cabinetry. SS Appliance package with built-in wine cooler. Two story living room with open rail leading to the upstairs, dining room has ship lapped accent wall! Get ready to be wowed!!! Primary bedroom is downstairs, barn doors lead into owner bath! Upstairs has 3 additional Bedrooms!
This home carries light thought-out! Large FENCED backyard!!! Place this home on your must see list!!!
